---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'

const effectiveDate = 'May 29, 2026'
const contactEmail = 'eligundry@gmail.com'
---

<Layout
  title="Methuselah · Terms and Conditions"
  description="Terms and conditions for Methuselah, Eli Gundry's personal SMS and email agent bot."
  fancyBackgroundPoints={10}
>
  <div class:list={['flex', 'flex-col', 'gap-y-4', 'prose', 'paper']}>
    <h1 class="mb-0">Methuselah Terms &amp; Conditions</h1>
    <p class="my-0"><em>Effective date: {effectiveDate}</em></p>

    <p>
      Methuselah is a personal AI agent operated by Eli Gundry that responds to
      text messages (SMS) and emails. It is a private hobby project used by me
      and my wife, not a commercial service offered to the public. By
      interacting with Methuselah, you agree to these terms.
    </p>

    <h2>The service</h2>
    <p>
      When you send a message or email to Methuselah, an automated agent reads
      it and sends back a reply. Responses are generated by AI and may be
      inaccurate, incomplete, or unexpected. Do not rely on Methuselah for
      emergencies, medical, legal, financial, or other professional advice.
    </p>

    <h2>Consent to receive messages</h2>
    <p>
      By providing your phone number and texting the service (or replying
      <strong>YES</strong> to a consent prompt), you consent to receive SMS messages
      from Methuselah. Consent is not a condition of any purchase. We will never
      share your number for third-party marketing.
    </p>

    <h2>Message frequency and rates</h2>
    <p>
      Message frequency varies based on your interactions with the agent.
      <strong>Message and data rates may apply</strong>, depending on your
      mobile carrier and plan. We are not responsible for any charges from your
      carrier.
    </p>

    <h2>Help and opting out</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>
        Reply <strong>HELP</strong> at any time for assistance, or email
        <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        Reply <strong>STOP</strong> at any time to opt out. You will receive a single
        confirmation message and then no further messages.
      </li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Acceptable use</h2>
    <p>
      Don't use Methuselah for anything unlawful, abusive, or harmful, and don't
      attempt to disrupt, overload, or misuse the service. Because this is a
      personal project, it is provided on a best-effort basis and may change or
      stop at any time without notice.
    </p>

    <h2>No warranty</h2>
    <p>
      Methuselah is provided "as is" and "as available," without warranties of
      any kind. To the fullest extent permitted by law, Eli Gundry is not liable
      for any damages arising from your use of, or inability to use, the
      service.
    </p>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Your use of Methuselah is also governed by the
      <a href="/methuselah/privacy-policy/">Privacy Policy</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
    <p>
      We may update these terms from time to time. Changes will be posted on
      this page with an updated effective date.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions? Email <a href={`mailto:${contactEmail}`}>{contactEmail}</a>.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
